<section class="primary-content">
  <p>We hold a member's only Chaingang session at <a href="https://goo.gl/maps/kUBu1DkFPxC2">Forge Valley School</a> on Tuesday evenings.</p>
  <p>Tuesday chaingang rides are there to perfect race craft and practice through and off at high speed. We use the Forge Valley circuit as it's a smooth tarmac, traffic environment but has points where riders can drop off the group and rejoin if the pace is too high.</p>
  <p>Chaingong costs £3 a week and is payable into the club's account. Speak to our <a href="mailto:racing@sitwell.cc">Racing Officer</a> about this.</p>
  <p>Please take time to read our <strong><a href="<%= asset_path('SitwellCyclingClubSitwellCCGenericRiskAssessment–RoadRides2016.pdf') %>">Risk Assessment</a> on Road Riding</strong>.</p>
  <h2 id="upcoming-rides">Upcoming rides</h2>
  <div id="rides">
    <% if (eventbrite.length > 0) { %>
      <ul>
        <% for(var i = 0; i < eventbrite.length; i++) { %>
          <li>
            <time class="post__date"><strong><%= eventbrite[i].date.day %> <%= eventbrite[i].date.date %> <%= eventbrite[i].date.month %> at <%= eventbrite[i].time %></strong></time>
          </li>
        <% } %>
      </ul>
    <% } else { %>
      <p>Sorry, we have no planned rides at present. Please check out our <a href="/club-rides/saturday-saunter">Saturday Saunter</a> or <a href="/club-rides/sunday-cafe-run">Sunday Café Run</a> rides.</p>
    <% } %>
  </div>
</section>

